episodes.title: MOTHER GOD: Cult Leaders, Scammers and Psychics on the Internet? (Ep 8)
episodes.description:
Hey! We’re your Rogue Therapists. Thanks for joining us to talk about all things psychology, pop culture, and the prime of our lives. 
💖 Remember, this isn’t clinical advice! We may be therapists, but we’re not your therapists. 
🪩 This is meant for entertainment and psychoeducation, and if you are in need of support, we recommend finding someone local to you. 
🗯️ We believe in the power of sharing your personal experiences, and know that true healing is best done when you are able to be your most authentic self.
🏳️‍🌈🏳️‍⚧️ While we come from positions of power and privilege, we want to acknowledge that and amplify the voices and stories of others around us. This is a safe space, affirming for all, regardless of how you identify and what you believe.
💭 Have something you want to say? Let us know! We’re accepting questions, comments and interview requests at our email address and social media accounts, listed below.
💌 ROGUETHERAPISTS@GMAIL.COM
🤍 TIKTOK: @ROGUETHERAPISTS
🗣️ YOUTUBE: @ROGUETHERAPISTS
👯‍♀️ INSTAGRAM: @ROGUETHERAPISTSPOD
